###############################################################################
###############################################################################
### NOTES & DOCUMENTATION
###############################################################################
###############################################################################

### API ENDPOINTS SUMMARY:
### 1. GET /api/jadwal/out-of-date   - Schedules past their deadline
### 2. GET /api/jadwal/active        - Schedules currently active (not overdue)
### 3. GET /api/jadwal/completed     - Schedules with status "Selesai" (3)
### 4. GET /api/jadwal/statistics    - Overall schedule statistics

### DEFAULT VALUES:
### out-of-date:
###   - limit: 20
###   - status_jadwal: 1,2
###   - sort_by: days_overdue
###   - sort_order: desc
###
### active:
###   - limit: 20
###   - status_jadwal: 1,2
###   - sort_by: tanggal_akhir
###   - sort_order: asc
###
### completed:
###   - limit: 20
###   - sort_by: tanggal_akhir
###   - sort_order: desc

### QUERY PARAMETERS:
### Common:
###   - limit (1-100)
###   - id_lsp (string)
###   - id_tuk (integer)
###   - sort_by (tanggal, tanggal_akhir, jadwal)
###   - sort_order (asc, desc)
###
### Active only:
###   - status_jadwal (0,1,2,3,4)
###   - days_until_end (integer)
###
### Completed only:
###   - date_from (YYYY-MM-DD)
###   - date_to (YYYY-MM-DD)

### RESPONSE FIELDS:
### out-of-date & active & completed:
###   - id, jadwal, tanggal, tanggal_akhir
###   - status_jadwal, status_label
###   - id_lsp, id_tuk, tuk
###
### active only:
###   - days_remaining (days until deadline)
###   - jumlah_asesi (nullable)
###   - asesor (nullable)
###
### out-of-date only:
###   - days_overdue (days past deadline)

### STATUS CODES:
### 0 = Draft/Baru
### 1 = Terjadwal
### 2 = Sedang Berlangsung
### 3 = Selesai
### 4 = Dibatalkan

### MOBILE APP USE CASES:
### Tab "Akan Berakhir":
###   GET /api/jadwal/active?status_jadwal=1,2&days_until_end=14&sort_by=tanggal_akhir&sort_order=asc
###
### Tab "Sedang Berjalan":
###   GET /api/jadwal/active?status_jadwal=2&sort_by=tanggal&sort_order=desc
###
### Tab "Selesai":
###   GET /api/jadwal/completed?limit=20&sort_by=tanggal_akhir&sort_order=desc

###############################################################################
s